= Information about OSSEC =

** Visit our website for the lasted news/information.
http://www.ossec.net/hids/

** This information is from version 0.1

OSSEC HIDS is a complex system that abstracts multiple host-based
intrusion detection capabilities into a single, scalable and
powerful infrascture. It includes log gathering, file integrity
checking, system health monitoring, event correlation and
analysis into a unique and powerfull tool.

